data.description: Charming Brick Home within walking distance to Wilson High School! Freshly painted walls and warm wood floors greet you upon entry. The sun filled living room with large bay window opens to a well appointed oak kitchen with access to a terrace overlooking the hillside of West Lawn.  Two bedrooms and a full bathroom complete the main level of the home. Upstairs awaits two additional guest bedrooms and a second full bathroom. The lower level of the home has been finished and offers a walk out entrance to the generously sized  backyard. A designated laundry space and half bathroom finalize this homes amenities.  Conveniently located close to schools, shopping and main travel ways this move in ready home is available for immediate possession!
